description: Daily maritime news covering marine, shipping and offshore updates from the global maritime industry. Sign-up for the daily maritime newsletter.
title: Global Maritime & Shipping News and Updates
maintext:
Middle East Report
Middle East Special Report 2024
There has been a flurry of investment in energy, ports, and logistics across the Middle East as well an international expansion of the region's leading maritime groups. Seatrade speaks to industry leaders about recent developments in the Middle East offshore and maritime industries, with an eye on future ambitions.
